   valuable insights into contextual factors and managerial strategies for
   leveraging relationship marketing investments. In an attempt to suggest
   normative guidelines to managers, we extend our analysis to a simple
   resource allocation model that describes the optimal mix of relationship
   marketing resources based on firm strategies.
